<i> I don't play.</i>

27:18.471 --> 27:20.604
Oh, you should listen.

27:20.606 --> 27:21.604
That's it.

27:21.641 --> 27:22.873
Don't make a mistake, emily.

27:22.942 --> 27:23.941
Oh!

27:23.943 --> 27:25.342
[splash]
[robin gasps]

27:26.445 --> 27:27.878
[laughing]

27:27.880 --> 27:29.213
Emily:
<i> That was a warning shot!</i>

27:29.348 --> 27:31.514
[laughing]

27:33.386 --> 27:34.851
Emily:
<i> What?!</i>

27:36.021 --> 27:37.287
Oh.

27:37.356 --> 27:38.621
[howard chuckles]

27:38.658 --> 27:40.290
You are crazy.
-Gotcha.

27:40.292 --> 27:41.725
You're crazy.

27:41.794 --> 27:42.926
Emily:
<i> You know you like it!</i>

27:42.995 --> 27:44.494
[laughing]

27:44.530 --> 27:45.495
Howard:
<i> I told you you should listen.</i>

27:45.564 --> 27:46.963
[laughing]

27:55.574 --> 27:57.174
What are we doing, velma?

