a life with her.

30:48.647 --> 30:51.748
<i> I don't want your sons</i>
<i> deaths to be for nothing.</i>

30:51.884 --> 30:56.153
[pensive music]

30:56.288 --> 30:58.054
[jean sighs]

31:06.398 --> 31:08.298
[marcie sighs]

31:10.035 --> 31:11.635
Before I make my ruling,

31:11.704 --> 31:14.304
Is there any additional
evidence to present?

