<i> Due to a lack of standing,</i>

31:26.285 --> 31:28.985
I have no choice but
to dismiss this case.

31:29.054 --> 31:32.189
They-they can't do this.

31:32.324 --> 31:33.790
[softy] they can't.

31:33.926 --> 31:35.058
I'm so sorry, trudy.

31:35.060 --> 31:37.461
[tense dramatic music]

31:37.596 --> 31:39.262
It's okay.

31:39.298 --> 31:46.203
[tense dramatic music]

31:46.338 --> 31:48.138
♪

31:51.944 --> 31:53.677
Marcie, come on.

