it all about her?

32:06.759 --> 32:08.091
I deserve that,
I get it.

32:08.093 --> 32:09.559
Yeah.

32:10.296 --> 32:11.762
Yes, you did.

32:11.897 --> 32:13.430
I miss you, okay?

32:13.499 --> 32:15.298
I know we said some rough
things to each other,

32:15.334 --> 32:16.833
But if there's a way
we can make this work,

32:16.969 --> 32:17.900
I'm willing to do that.

32:17.937 --> 32:19.402
Don't, just...

32:20.673 --> 32:22.138
Don't.

32:24.343 --> 32:26.176
Marcie, there's a
lot of good here.

32:28.147 --> 32:29.579
Between us.

32:31.850 --> 32:33.449
[phone vibrates]

32:35.988 --> 32:37.821
See you at the wedding.

32:40.159 --> 32:41.324
Hello.

32:41.327 --> 32:43.926
Audra:
<i> Hey marcie,</i>
<i> it's audra alward.</i>

32:43.963 --> 32:45.595
Oh, hey, audra.

32:45.731 --> 32:48.798
Audra:
<i> I'm wondering if it's possible</i>
<i> we could meet this afternoon?</i>

32:48.867 --> 32:49.800
Actually, you know what?

32:49.935 --> 32:52.602
