a friend's wedding.

32:52.671 --> 32:54.271
Audra:
<i> Marcie, it's important.</i>

32:54.273 --> 32:56.806
We might have a solution to
your ezra elvins problem.

32:58.911 --> 33:00.410
Of course.

33:00.412 --> 33:01.945
No secrets in this town.

33:02.748 --> 33:05.681
Ah, when?

33:07.419 --> 33:10.153
Okay, thirty minutes
is great.

33:10.288 --> 33:11.721
Okay.

33:18.764 --> 33:20.363
What are you doing here?

33:20.432 --> 33:23.867
