34:01.673 --> 34:02.672
Michelle:
<i> Oh, I will.</i>

34:02.674 --> 34:04.140
Trust me.

34:04.877 --> 34:05.542
[gentle background vocals]

34:05.611 --> 34:06.643
Hi!

34:06.778 --> 34:08.211
Oh!

34:09.314 --> 34:11.548
