really want me there?

34:22.961 --> 34:23.960
Hey!
-Hi.

34:23.962 --> 34:25.829
Good to see you.

34:25.831 --> 34:27.563
Hi.

34:27.599 --> 34:29.566
I am so happy for you guys.

34:29.635 --> 34:31.734
I'm so glad you came.

34:31.804 --> 34:35.572
<i> ♪ as the sun sinks low ♪</i>

34:35.574 --> 34:36.973
Hi!
-Hi!

34:37.943 --> 34:38.842
