Yeah, right?

37:20.939 --> 37:22.539
Her loss.

37:22.674 --> 37:24.440
Thanks, dad. I love you.

37:25.777 --> 37:27.010
Hey.

37:27.079 --> 37:28.344
Oh, hey.

37:28.479 --> 37:29.445
